msgstr "ອັບເດດຜູ້ຖືບັດສຳເລັດແລ້ວ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/product_mcc_stripe_tag.py:0
msgid ""
"The MCC code '%(code)s' is not valid. It must be either a 4-digit code or a "
"range in the format 'XXXX-XXXX'."
msgstr "ລະຫັດ MCC '%(code)s' ບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ. ຕ້ອງເປັນລະຫັດ 4 ໂຕ ຫຼື ຊ່ວງໃນຮູບແບບ 'XXXX-XXXX'."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/utils.py:0
msgid ""
"The Stripe account specified in the request wasn't found. Please check your "
"configuration"
msgstr "ບໍ່ພົບບັນຊີ Stripe ທີ່ລະບຸໃນຄຳຮ້ອງຂໍ. ກະລຸນາກວດສອບການຕັ້ງຄ່າຂອງທ່ານ"

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense_stripe_card.py:0
msgid ""
"The Stripe issuing account isn't properly set. Please connect to Stripe in "
"the settings"
msgstr "ບໍ່ໄດ້ຕັ້ງຄ່າບັນຊີ Stripe issuing ຢ່າງຖືກຕ້ອງ. ກະລຸນາເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ Stripe ໃນການຕັ້ງຄ່າ"

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense_stripe_card.py:0
msgid "The Stripe public key is missing"
msgstr "Stripe public key ຫາຍໄປ"

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:hr_expense_stripe.field_hr_expense_stripe_card__delivery_address_id
msgid "The address where the card will be delivered."
msgstr "ທີ່ຢູ່ທີ່ຈະຈັດສົ່ງບັດ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/utils.py:0
msgid "The authorization failed required verification checks."
msgstr "ການອະນຸມັດລົ້ມເຫຼວເນື່ອງຈາກບໍ່ຜ່ານການກວດສອບທີ່ຈຳເປັນ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/controllers/main.py:0
msgid ""
"The authorization was approved by the webhook, but was later reversed or "
"closed without any capture."
msgstr ""
"ການອະນຸມັດໄດ້ຮັບການຍອມຮັບໂດຍ Webhook ແລ້ວ, ແຕ່ຕໍ່ມາຖືກດຶງຄືນ ຫຼື ປິດລົງໂດຍບໍ່ມີການຕັດຍອດເງິນ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/utils.py:0
msgid "The authorization was approved by your Odoo database."
msgstr "ການອະນຸມັດໄດ້ຮັບການຍອມຮັບໂດຍຖານຂໍ້ມູນ Odoo ຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/utils.py:0
msgid "The authorization was refused by your Odoo database."
msgstr "ການອະນຸມັດຖືກປະຕິເສດໂດຍຖານຂໍ້ມູນ Odoo ຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/utils.py:0
msgid ""
"The authorization was suspected as fraudulent by Stripe's risk controls."
msgstr "ການອະນຸມັດຖືກສົງໄສວ່າເປັນການສໍ້ໂກງໂດຍລະບົບຄວບຄຸມຄວາມສ່ຽງຂອງ Stripe."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/utils.py:0
msgid "The card has expired."
msgstr "ບັດໝົດອາຍຸແລ້ວ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/utils.py:0
msgid ""
"The card is active, and there was no control setup on your Stripe account."
msgstr "ບັດໃຊ້ງານໄດ້ປົກກະຕິ, ແລະ ບໍ່ມີການຕັ້ງຄ່າຄວບຄຸມໃນບັນຊີ Stripe ຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/utils.py:0
msgid "The card is currently inactive, please activate it first."
msgstr "ໃນປັດຈຸບັນບັດຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ເປີດໃຊ້, ກະລຸນາເປີດໃຊ້ບັດກ່ອນ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense_stripe_card.py:0
msgid "The card must be ordered by a user."
msgstr "ບັດຕ້ອງຖືກສັ່ງໂດຍຜູ້ໃຊ້."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense_stripe_card.py:0
msgid "The card must have a delivery date if it is marked as delivered."
msgstr "ບັດຕ້ອງມີວັນທີຈັດສົ່ງຫາກຖືກໝາຍວ່າຈັດສົ່ງແລ້ວ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/utils.py:0
msgid "The card used was blocked."
msgstr "ບັດທີ່ໃຊ້ຖືກລະງັບແລ້ວ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/wizard/hr_expense_stripe_card_block_wizard.py:0
msgid ""
"The card was blocked for the following reason:\n"
"%(reason)s"
msgstr ""
"ບັດຖືກລະງັບຍ້ອນເຫດຜົນດັ່ງນີ້:\n"
"%(reason)s"

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/utils.py:0
msgid "The card was declined because of the Stripe spending controls."
msgstr "ບັດຖືກປະຕິເສດເນື່ອງຈາກການຄວບຄຸມການໃຊ້ຈ່າຍຂອງ Stripe."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/utils.py:0
msgid "The card's PIN is blocked."
msgstr "ລະຫັດ PIN ຂອງບັດຖືກລະງັບແລ້ວ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#: model:mail.message.subtype,description:hr_expense_stripe.mt_stripe_cardholder_updated
msgid "The cardholder data was updated on Stripe"
msgstr "ຂໍ້ມູນຜູ້ຖືບັດໄດ້ຮັບການອັບເດດໃນ Stripe ແລ້ວ"

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/utils.py:0
msgid "The cardholder is currently inactive."
msgstr "ຜູ້ຖືບັດໃນປັດຈຸບັນບໍ່ມີການເຄື່ອນໄຫວ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/utils.py:0
msgid "The cardholder is still under verification."
msgstr "ຜູ້ຖືບັດຍັງຢູ່ໃນຂັ້ນຕອນການກວດສອບ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/utils.py:0
msgid "The cardholder was blocked."
msgstr "ຜູ້ຖືບັດຖືກລະງັບແລ້ວ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/utils.py:0
msgid ""
"The charge is not allowed on the Stripe network, possibly because it is an "
"ATM withdrawal or cash advance."
msgstr ""
"ບໍ່ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ຕັດຍອດເງິນໃນເຄືອຂ່າຍ Stripe, ອາດຈະເປັນຍ້ອນວ່າມັນແມ່ນການຖອນເງິນຈາກຕູ້ ATM ຫຼື "
"ການເບີກເງິນສົດລ່ວງໜ້າ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#: model:ir.model.constraint,message:hr_expense_stripe.constraint_product_mcc_stripe_tag_constraint_code_unique
msgid "The code of the MCC tag must be unique!"
msgstr "ລະຫັດຂອງແທັກ MCC ຕ້ອງບໍ່ຊ້ຳກັນ!"

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense_stripe_card.py:0
msgid "The code to access your Odoo Expense Card is: %(code)s"
msgstr "ລະຫັດເພື່ອເຂົ້າເຖິງບັດ Odoo Expense ຂອງທ່ານແມ່ນ: %(code)s"

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/utils.py:0
msgid "The country of the phone number is not supported for SMS."
msgstr "ປະເທດຂອງເບີໂທລະສັບນີ້ຍັງບໍ່ຮອງຮັບການສົ່ງ SMS."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/utils.py:0
msgid ""
"The creation rate limit for this type of cards has been reached. Please try "
"again later."
msgstr "ຂີດຈຳກັດໃນການສ້າງບັດປະເພດນີ້ເຕັມແລ້ວ. ກະລຸນາລອງໃໝ່ພາຍຫຼັງ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense_stripe_card.py:0
msgid ""
"The delivery address must be in the European Union or in the United Kingdom."
msgstr "ທີ່ຢູ່ຈັດສົ່ງຕ້ອງຢູ່ໃນສະຫະພາບເອີຣົບ ຫຼື ສະຫະລາຊະອານາຈັກ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense_stripe_card.py:0
msgid "The delivery address must be in the European Union."
msgstr "ທີ່ຢູ່ຈັດສົ່ງຕ້ອງຢູ່ໃນສະຫະພາບເອີຣົບ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense_stripe_card.py:0
msgid "The delivery address must be set before activating the card."
msgstr "ຕ້ອງຕັ້ງທີ່ຢູ່ຈັດສົ່ງກ່ອນເປີດໃຊ້ບັດ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense_stripe_card.py:0
msgid ""
"The delivery address must have a street, city, zip code and country set."
msgstr "ທີ່ຢູ່ຈັດສົ່ງຕ້ອງລະບຸຖະໜົນ, ເມືອງ, ລະຫັດໄປສະນີ ແລະ ປະເທດ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/wizard/hr_expense_stripe_topup_wizard.py:0
msgid "The direct top-up isn't available outside of the US."
msgstr "ການເຕີມເງິນໂດຍກົງຍັງບໍ່ເປີດໃຫ້ບໍລິການຢູ່ນອກສະຫະລັດ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense_stripe_card.py:0
msgid "The employee must have a user to be able to access safely their card."
msgstr "ພະນັກງານຕ້ອງມີບັນຊີຜູ້ໃຊ້ເພື່ອເຂົ້າເຖິງບັດຂອງເຂົາເຈົ້າໄດ້ຢ່າງປອດໄພ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:hr_expense_stripe.field_hr_expense_stripe_card_receive_wizard__last_4_challenge
msgid ""
"The last 4 digits of the card you received. This is used to confirm that you "
"have received the correct card."
msgstr "ເລກ 4 ໂຕສຸດທ້າຍຂອງບັດທີ່ທ່ານໄດ້ຮັບ. ໃຊ້ເພື່ອຢືນຢັນວ່າທ່ານໄດ້ຮັບບັດທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/wizard/hr_expense_stripe_card_receive_wizard.py:0
msgid ""
"The last 4 digits you entered do not match the card you received. Please "
"check and try again."
msgstr "ເລກ 4 ໂຕສຸດທ້າຍທີ່ທ່ານປ້ອນບໍ່ກົງກັບບັດທີ່ທ່ານໄດ້ຮັບ. ກະລຸນາກວດສອບ ແລະ ລອງໃໝ່ອີກຄັ້ງ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:hr_expense_stripe.field_hr_expense_stripe_card__card_name
msgid "The name displayed on the card"
msgstr "ຊື່ທີ່ສະແດງຢູ່ໃນບັດ"

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense_stripe_card.py:0
msgid ""
"The phone number associated with your Odoo Expense card(s) has been updated. "
"If it was not requested by you, please contact your administrator."
msgstr ""
"ເບີໂທລະສັບທີ່ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ກັບບັດ Odoo Expense ຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຮັບການອັບເດດແລ້ວ. ຫາກທ່ານບໍ່ໄດ້ເປັນຜູ້ຮ້ອງຂໍ, "
"ກະລຸນາຕິດຕໍ່ຜູ້ດູແລລະບົບ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/wizard/hr_expense_stripe_cardholder_wizard.py:0
msgid "The phone number is invalid."
msgstr "ເບີໂທລະສັບບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/utils.py:0
msgid ""
"The route '%(route)s' is not allowed to be called from the Stripe IAP proxy "
"server."
msgstr "ບໍ່ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ເອີ້ນໃຊ້ເສັ້ນທາງ '%(route)s' ຈາກເຊີເວີພຣັອກຊີ Stripe IAP."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/utils.py:0
msgid ""
"The sms service is currently experiencing a lot of request. Please try again "
"in a few minutes."
msgstr "ບໍລິການ SMS ກຳລັງມີຄຳຮ້ອງຂໍຈຳນວນຫຼາຍ. ກະລຸນາລອງໃໝ່ໃນອີກບໍ່ເທົ່າໃດນາທີ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hr_expense_stripe.view_hr_expense_stripe_card_form
msgid ""
"The spending limits set on this card are higher than the limits set by "
"Stripe of 50.000 per day and per transaction."
msgstr ""
"ຂີດຈຳກັດການໃຊ້ຈ່າຍທີ່ຕັ້ງໄວ້ໃນບັດນີ້ສູງກວ່າຂີດຈຳກັດຂອງ Stripe ທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ 50,000 ຕໍ່ມື້ ແລະ ຕໍ່ທຸລະກຳ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/wizard/hr_expense_stripe_topup_wizard.py:0
msgid "The statement description can only contain 15 ASCII characters"
msgstr "ຄຳອະທິບາຍລາຍການສາມາດມີຕົວອັກສອນ ASCII ໄດ້ສູງສຸດ 15 ຕົວ"

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#: model:product.mcc.stripe.tag,name:hr_expense_stripe.theatrical_ticket_agencies
msgid "Theatrical Ticket Agencies"
msgstr "ຕົວແທນຈຳໜ່າຍບັດເຂົ້າຊົມການສະແດງ"

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/utils.py:0
msgid ""
"There is insufficient funds on your Stripe account, please top-up your "
"account first."
msgstr "ເງິນໃນບັນຊີ Stripe ຂອງທ່ານບໍ່ພຽງພໍ, ກະລຸນາເຕີມເງິນກ່ອນ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense.py:0
msgid ""
"There is no product available for this expense. Please contact your "
"administrator."
msgstr "ບໍ່ມີຜະລິດຕະພັນສຳລັບລາຍຈ່າຍນີ້. ກະລຸນາຕິດຕໍ່ຜູ້ດູແລລະບົບ."

