"You can't change the employee of an active card. Please create a new card "
"instead."
msgstr "ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດປ່ຽນພະນັກງານຂອງບັດທີ່ກຳລັງໃຊ້ງານຢູ່. ກະລຸນາສ້າງບັດໃໝ່ແທນ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense_stripe_card.py:0
