"You cannot delete a payment method line that is used by an active/paused "
"card."
msgstr "ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດລຶບວິທີການຊຳລະເງິນທີ່ຖືກໃຊ້ໂດຍບັດທີ່ໃຊ້ງານຢູ່ ຫຼື ຢຸດຊົ່ວຄາວ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense.py:0
msgid ""
"You cannot delete an expense that was created from a Stripe card transaction."
msgstr "ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດລຶບລາຍຈ່າຍທີ່ສ້າງຂຶ້ນຈາກທຸລະກຳບັດ Stripe ໄດ້."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense.py:0
