"You cannot set a cost on a product that is used as an Expense card category. "
"Please duplicate it instead."
msgstr "ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດຕັ້ງຕົ້ນທຶນໃຫ້ກັບຜະລິດຕະພັນທີ່ໃຊ້ເປັນໝວດໝູ່ບັດລາຍຈ່າຍ. ກະລຸນາສ້າງຊ້ຳແທນ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense.py:0
msgid ""
"You cannot split an expense that is reserved. Please wait for the "
"transaction to be captured."
msgstr "ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດແບ່ງລາຍຈ່າຍທີ່ຖືກຈອງໄວ້. ກະລຸນາລໍຖ້າໃຫ້ທຸລະກຳຖືກຕັດຍອດກ່ອນ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense.py:0
msgid ""
"You cannot submit an expense that is reserved. Please wait for the "
"transaction to be captured."
msgstr "ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດສົ່ງລາຍຈ່າຍທີ່ຖືກຈອງໄວ້. ກະລຸນາລໍຖ້າໃຫ້ທຸລະກຳຖືກຕັດຍອດກ່ອນ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/__init__.py:0
