"You cannot uninstall the 'Expense cards' module while there are active or "
"inactive Stripe cards. Please manually block all cards before uninstalling "
"the module."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດຖອນການຕິດຕັ້ງໂມດູນ 'Expense cards' ໃນຂະນະທີ່ມີບັດ Stripe ທີ່ກຳລັງໃຊ້ງານ ຫຼື "
"ບໍ່ໄດ້ໃຊ້ງານ. ກະລຸນາລະງັບບັດທັງໝົດກ່ອນຖອນການຕິດຕັ້ງ."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/static/src/components/open_card_receive_terms.xml:0
